data.description: This 4-bed, 3-bath home in San Tan Valley is finally on the market! Two-story property with desert landscaping and a two-car garage. Light & bright open layout boasting wood-look tile flooring throughout the main level, a neutral palette, and gorgeous light fixtures. Cook delicious meals in the immaculate kitchen equipped with built-in appliances, white cabinets, ample counter space, and a peninsula with a breakfast bar. Upstairs, discover soft carpet underfoot and a large loft ideal for a game area! The primary retreat offers an ensuite with a double sink vanity and a mirrored door walk-in closet. The downstairs bedroom & full bathroom are perfect for guests! Relax in the peaceful backyard featuring a covered patio and grass. This beauty is sure to sell fast!
